OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHate faced by MP is attack 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fon democracy, says No 10   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Downing Street has said the "vitriolic 
OL,6, hatred" faced by a Tory MP who has said
OL,7, he will stand down at the next election
OL,8, is an "attack on British democracy".   
OL,10,FDeath threats and an alleged arson     
OL,11,Fattack on his constituency office had  
OL,12,F"become too much", Justice Minister    
OL,13,FMike Freer told the Daily Mail.        
OL,15,FThe PM's spokesman said no one elected 
OL,16,F"deserves to be abused or intimidated".
OL,18,FAsked if MPs had enough protection, the
OL,19,Fspokesman added existing measures were 
OL,20,F"robust" but were "kept under review". 
